OL,3,CTwo men charged with violent disorder
OL,4,Cafter double stabbing
OL,6,FTwo men who were injured in the
OL,7,Fincident were taken to hospital and
OL,8,Fremain in a stable condition.
OL,10,FHala and Kola are both due to appear
OL,11,Fat the North Staffordshire Justice
OL,12,FCentre today.
OL,14,FA 26-year-old man, from Stoke-on-
OL,15,FTrent, who was also arrested in
OL,16,Fconnection with the incident, has
OL,17,Fsince been bailed with conditions.
